result.name: Umimachi Don

reviews.text: Fun way of eating kaisen don: each bowl comes with vinegar jelly and fish soup so you can experience it three ways! Fish is fresh and high quality, and affordable too.

One of the best seafood don in Hong Kong
The crab is so good along with their signature vinegar jelly!

Got really sick afterwards
Food poisoning 
Not very clean establishment
A quiet Japanese restaurant, you can traditional Don rice here.

Quaint Japanese restaurant in Quarry Bay that specializes is sushi rice sets. They offer a standard, deluxe and premium options where the premium has more expensive ingredients like unit and shrimp. For the non sashimi eaters they do offer egg donburi options. 

The seating at this place is fairly limited, but the turnover is fast. Recommend for a quick and affordable bite to eat. 

Food: 4 stars
Environment/service: 3.5 stars 
Value: 5 stars

reviews.text: 味道不錯！足料！加飯變大盛，也不用加價，烏龍茶和味噌湯好喝。配上獨有的咸咸的jelly，魚生別有一番風味 (如果吃不慣咸，先淺嚐一小口為佳)
Fun way of eating kaisen don: each bowl comes with vinegar jelly and fish soup so you can experience it three ways! Fish is fresh and high quality, and affordable too.
我鍾意個壽司醋啫喱，整體味道唔錯，最後可以加湯做茶漬飯，個凍辣番茄個汁幾得意，可以一試

One of the best seafood don in Hong Kong
The crab is so good along with their signature vinegar jelly!
魚生飯都算吾錯, 午餐未試到店鋪既功力, 會再試晚餐.
